            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>soured cream</strong>, <strong>chopped shallot </strong>and <strong>chopped dill</strong> in a small bowl</p><p>Add a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper </strong>and stir it all together – this is your<strong> dill sauce</strong></p><p>Once the prawns have cooled, stir the <strong>cooked prawns </strong>through the <strong>dill sauce </strong>– this is your <strong>Scandinavian-style king prawn skagen</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
