    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice your <strong>ciabatta[s]</strong> into 3<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>thin slices per person</p><p>Once the potatoes are beginning to crisp, remove the tray from the oven and add the <strong>sliced ciabatta </strong>to the tray with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Put the tray back in the oven for a final 5-7 min or until golden and crisp</p>",
